{"tid":1751563,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"何鳩搖 輸咗 請舉出四字詞語恭賀說話","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:58:09.000Z","uid":242537,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"0316fd62013dd02ce809688112580b4d3a84e27b","tid":1751563,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"熱烈彈琴<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div><br />\n<br />\n曲：五輪真弓 | 詞：鄭國江 | 編：吳智強<br />\n<br />\n齊鼓掌(高歌) 歌聲放今晚開心唱請鼓掌<br />\n齊鼓掌(高歌) 歌聲唱今晚開心唱請欣賞<br />\n熱鬧情調盡情又放量<br />\n人人陶醉熱情狀雙雙對對共欣賞<br />\n<br />\n熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱<br />\n歌聲多奔放個個喜氣洋洋<br />\n飲多杯祝你個個都開心歡暢<br />\n(飲多杯勝嘅各位乾杯飲勝)<br />\n喜氣洋洋 洋溢四方<br />\n<br />\n熱熱鬧鬧燈正亮酒正香<br />\n滿室鬢影衣香<br />\n愉快暢聚 我願你哋快樂同分享<br />\n為你快樂歌唱 歡笑莫嫌良夜長<br />\n願你我和唱 愉快渡快樂時光<br />\n渡快樂時光 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FK53R0fnH-E&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFK53R0fnH-E%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb60IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=c6ca6641\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FK53R0fnH-E&amp;feature=emb_logo</a>"},{"pid":"8ea17930f13baada308f086696b8d3424de93873","tid":1751563,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe0ea011035bd59802579f3a0bf5bd2ccb0f36","tid":1751563,"uid":277644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊.jpg"},{"pid":"aa70bdf1a136888cc700a6ec66e649c0284de7e1","tid":1751563,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"85fe0ea011035bd59802579f3a0bf5bd2ccb0f36","tid":1751563,"uid":277644,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊.jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"四字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so